summary: This is female body replacer. It will change the way every naked female will look ingame.
descriptionHtml:
[CENTER][IMG]http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/imageshare/supporters/images/537675-1329051050.png[/IMG]

Moderated by dimon99,Lyre2r14 and Vectorcide

IMPORTANT: Guys, do not send PM\'s to me (dimon99) - I do not have a computer ATM (as pretty much most things) -  thanks to hurricane Sandy.  Thanks and see ya all later.  ALL my mods are now FREE TO MOD,since I am unreacheable.

Hello folks, it\'s been awhile since I uploaded anything to the public. But I think Skyrim is great game, probably the best Beth\'s game since Morrowind, and I glad to see big improvements in skeleton,animations and body models. So,I think I\'m gonna be interested in Skyrim for a long time. Thus, this mod. Which does NOT pretend to be: realistic,beautiful,eyecandy,it even does not pretend to be human-like. Just something I making to suit my tastes. So,here it is -UNPRETENDED. PLEASE refrain from any kind of negative comments on other mods in discussion thread. You can lay as much shitte as you want on my mod in that thread - but that\'s it, nothing else ;)[/CENTER]

[IMG]http://playvampire.com/images/skyrim/features.png[/IMG]

[img]http://playvampire.com/images/skyrim/splatter.png[/img]Greatly improved feet meshes, seamless hands and feet textures, high quality body textures and mesh.
[img]http://playvampire.com/images/skyrim/splatter.png[/img]Two variants, BASE and SKINNY. Base covers from Slim to Pinup and Skinny covers A cup to C cup.
[img]http://playvampire.com/images/skyrim/splatter.png[/img]Pubic hair options - Bushy (Pubic1), Bushy lite (Pubic1L), Trimmed (Pubic2) and Shaved.
[img]http://playvampire.com/images/skyrim/splatter.png[/img]SFW bikini meshes and textures - Optional more cloth-like or silky textures in Miscellaneous downloads.

[IMG]http://playvampire.com/images/skyrim/faq.png[/IMG]

[img]http://playvampire.com/images/skyrim/splatter.png[/img] [b][color=#b397c7]Will you upload to Steam Workshop?[/b][/color] When Exeter finishes with vanilla armor replacer, when I finish with textures, ect ect, we (modders, who support UNP) will decide-worth it or not.

[img]http://playvampire.com/images/skyrim/splatter.png[/img] [b][color=#b397c7]The texture looks blocky and bad, can you make higher resolution ones?[/b][/color] Look under OPTIONAL FILES in the downloads area for HD Normal maps for UNP BASE bodies.

[img]http://playvampire.com/images/skyrim/splatter.png[/img] [b][color=#b397c7]Do old women have the same bodies as young women?[/b][/color] Yes. Bethesda didn\'t code in different meshes for races or ages so Modders are only able to work within that limitation. All females in the game will have the same body changed only by the weight slider.

[IMG]http://playvampire.com/images/skyrim/compatible.png[/IMG]

Many clothes and armors made for other bodies can still be used with UNP, your character will just change shape when wearing it instead of having the body she has when naked. For a list of mods that fit the UNP shape visit the [URL=http://forums.nexusmods.com/index.php?showtopic=550519][color=#f2f2f2][u]list of compatible mods on Nexus[/u][/color][/URL]. ( Feel free to add anything you find yourself) *Tip: Search UNP in the Nexus search box.

[img]http://playvampire.com/images/skyrim/splatter.png[/img] Exeter has a WIP to convert all vanilla armors and clothing to UNP. [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=7305][color=#f2f2f2][u]Download his mod![/u][/color][/url]
[img]http://playvampire.com/images/skyrim/splatter.png[/img] Skimpy versions of many vanilla armors can be [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=9546][color=#f2f2f2][u]downloaded here[/u][/color][/url].
For more athletic look -check out this mod,it looks good http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=13377

XCE is [u]incompatible[/u] and will cause texture issues!

[IMG]http://playvampire.com/images/skyrim/install.png[/IMG]

To be safe - backup these two folders so if you don\'t like my mod, you can easily revert to whatever you had before:
* Data\\textures\\actors\\character\\female
* Data\\meshes\\actors\\character\\character assets
Delete any files from a previous body replacer to avoid conflicts.

[img]http://playvampire.com/images/skyrim/splatter.png[/img] [color=#b397c7][b]1)[/b][/color] Choose either UNP BASE Main body V1dot2 or UNP BASE Skinny body V1dot2 (Not both!)
[img]http://playvampire.com/images/skyrim/splatter.png[/img] [color=#b397c7][b]2)[/b][/color] Download and unzip/unrar into Data folder (default ...steam/steamapps/common/skyrim/data) 
[img]http://playvampire.com/images/skyrim/splatter.png[/img] [color=#b397c7][b]OPTIONAL[/b][/color] If you want the optional SFW Bikinis download SFW bikinis for Main body. If you are using Skinny, you\'ll need to then download SFW bikinis for Skinny body and install on top of Main.
[img]http://playvampire.com/images/skyrim/splatter.png[/img] [color=#b397c7][b]OPTIONAL[/b][/color] If you find the textures to be blocky or have strange lines under OPTIONAL FILES and install HD Normal maps for UNP BASE bodies.

[IMG]http://playvampire.com/images/skyrim/issues.png[/IMG]

[img]http://playvampire.com/images/skyrim/splatter.png[/img] [color=#b397c7][b]FIX FOR BETHESDA HIGH QUALITY TEXTURES[/b][/color] Beth HD texture pack will OVERRIDE UNP textures, and body will look like CRAP. To fix it follow the steps here: [URL=http://forums.nexusmods.com/index.php?showtopic=557650][color=#f2f2f2][u]Fix for Beth HD texture pack - The Nexus Forums[/u][/color][/URL]

[img]http://playvampire.com/images/skyrim/splatter.png[/img] [color=#b397c7][b]CTD WHEN USING BIKINIS[/b][/color] For those experiencing CTD with bikinis, FIX1 is in the downloads.

[img]http://playvampire.com/images/skyrim/splatter.png[/img] [color=#b397c7][b]NECK SEAM SOLUTIONS[/b][/color]

PLEASE NOTE - It is a common bug with NPC\'s that the face and body textures will not match. To fix this open the console ` select the npc with the mouse and type setnpcweight (1-100). This will adjust the NPC and fix the issue. For your own characters try one of the solutions below.

* [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=3563][color=#f2f2f2][u]Coverwomen[/u][/color][/url] - MrLenski has UNP compatible face textures under optional downloads
* Vanilla - Try [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=6554][color=#f2f2f2][u]Thepal\'s[/u][/color][/url] UNP compatible body texture
* [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=6953][color=#f2f2f2][u]Oriental Beauty Face Mod[/u][/color][/url] has been reported to have little to no seam.
* Photoshop Users - Under Misc files is a .psd that you can use to make UNP compatible with ANY custom face texture. Read the [url=http://forums.nexusmods.com/index.php?showtopic=597488][color=#f2f2f2][u]tutorial here[/u][/color][/url].

[IMG]http://playvampire.com/images/skyrim/plans.png[/IMG]

* Texture improvements and variants, like pubic hairs ect ect
* More normal map variants - A PDF file in the Misc downloads allows some quick customization (Photoshop knowledge required! For advanced users only)
* Dedicated A Cup model and textures.- Half done
* Specialized \"custom\" bodies.- These can wait for now. Not that I\'m not making them anyway ;)

[IMG]http://playvampire.com/images/skyrim/changelog.png[/IMG]

[color=#b397c7]Version 1.3[/color]
V1.51 All pubic variants are brought up to latest version. There was some cleaning and spot healing in troublesome spots. Feet were fully textured as well. 
  These will be the main UNP textures for AWHILE. Pretty much whole body is textured properly now. 
V1.5 DIMface2 optional face textures are up. README inside.
V1.31 TEST RUN: New boobs variant for heavy end of Main body. Advanced users only.
V1.3 UPDATE: Shaved texture is up, genitals are in,whole area is reworked and brought together. w00t!

[color=#b397c7]Version 1.2[/color]

V1.21Update Pubic hairs are up.
V1.2addon T_emu1. Released currently as a clothing RESOURCE,not as a finished thing. Meshes are good,textures are crap and weights are so-so. If installed \"as is\" - it replaces Glass armor cuirass.All details in README
V1.2 FIX1 Here\'s quick fix for bikini CTD,try it. I didn\'t CTD by equipping/unequipping or zonong, but I had a save ,that wouldn\'t load and game CTD on load. This FIX eliminated the problem. Manual install. Meshes only,both for Main and Skinny. 
V1.2Final UPDATE: Bikinis for Skinny body are up. Wasn\'t planned,but was requested by modders.
Namely nippless and \"bra\" boobs bodymeshes,which are in this package. Meshes only,get bikini textures from Main bikinis,then install these meshes.
V1.2 addon SDress modding resource is up,along with modified n-maps for bikinis
V1.2UPDATE(cont) Meshes for Main and Skinny with updated rigging are up. NOT a required update for players or modders. Just use these for future projects,they animate better. Also, fixed a small symmetry bug with Heavy PUSHUP Boobs mesh,used for clothemaking. Meshes are up. And this concludes V1.2 RIGFIX Update.
V1.2 addon PDF with Neck textures is up. Blend these with your face texture to reduce the seam.
V1.2 UPDATE  RIGFIX1 /Undies
Not much for players,just undies,but a big update for me and noticeable for modders.
Undies readme:Update contains undies (SFW bikinis), by default, dark bikinis will install. In OPTION folder there\'s WHITE bikinis textures. Just drop and \"yes\" overwrite in Data\\textures\\actors\\character\\female , just one texture has to be overwritten. You have to do this by hand,no managers
For modders:
Much more then bikinis in this update- rigging,the way body animates,was improved. Under bikinis there are first 2 body meshes with improved weights. These are the most desireable for new outfits projects. They just gonna animate better. No need to do ANYTHING with completed outfits.Do NOT update anything.No need,really.Just use new meshes for future projects. 
All \"nude\" meshes will be upgraded with new weights eventually. 

[color=#b397c7]Version 1.1[/color]

V1.1 Addon.  Ucompressed normal maps for BASE bodies are UP. No cubes,no artifacts.
V1.1-UPDATE. Main BASE body is up. Covers range from Slim to Heavy (pinup). I plan to use it as overall replacer,NPCs should look more balanced (when in UNP-fitted clothes,which is NONE currently,hehe) IMO. All needed meshes/textures included.
    Skinny BASE body is up. Covers ranges from petite frame, A Cup, to Normal BASE mesh,around C Cup.
Again,all in one package,everything released so far is included, Normal map is optimised for smaller boobs,they will look more natural. Bigger boobs may look flat. 
V1dot1b -Tiny update, vanilla hands with some fixes, so there\'s much less seam between body and hands. Kudos to Zentard for pinpointing the issue!

[color=#b397c7]Version 1.0 [/color]

V1dot0 -initial release: Only one body variant for now: BASE \"normal to heavy pinup\". No head textures yet-I\'m waiting for permissions...will release as soon as I get replies, or make my own maps.

[IMG]http://playvampire.com/images/skyrim/credits.png[/IMG]

*Bethesda - base mesh for the body model, specular and normal maps.
*Phygit- feet model and normal map [URL=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=3666][color=#f2f2f2][u]FemFeet at Skyrim Nexus - Skyrim Mods and community[/u][/color][/URL]
*Thepal - body normal map edit
*jclyde6108 - proper skeleton for rigging [URL=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=7524][color=#f2f2f2][u]UNP Skeleton Resource at Skyrim Nexus - Skyrim Mods and community[/u][/color][/URL]

Special thanks to:

Mods used in my images:
FavoredSouls Angels in Skyrim by FavoredSoul  http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=10658
Velvec Outfit - UNP by anano  http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=10211

Thanks!

[IMG]http://playvampire.com/images/skyrim/legal.png[/IMG]
 Any customizations to all textures and meshes are now ALLOWED on these terms: you cannot claim it as your own, credit and link to original are REQUIRED.

Feet meshes-contact the author, Phygit

Everything else is free to modify on these conditions: upload at Nexus and give proper credits and link to original mod. No permission required.
